**Testing From Main Menu Scene:**

- Find the “BodyPartLocationsAndSetUp” object , which is a child of the eqvr\_HORSE\_ gameobject.![][image1]  
- Once selected, You should see the Body Part Setup Component in the Inspector, Turn off Debug Mode so the scenario will use the selections from the main menu rather then this component.

![][image2]

**Testing From Clinic Scene:**

- Find the “BodyPartLocationsAndSetUp” object , which is a child of the eqvr\_HORSE\_ gameobject.![][image1]  
- Once selected, You should see the Body Part Setup Component in the Inspector, Turn on Debug Mode , and select the xray type, body part and leg selection you wish to test.

![][image2]

**Summary**: When testing from the **main menu** the **debug mode** should be **off**, when testing from the **clinic scene** **debug mode** should be **on** and selections should be set in the component.
